Sealed pots of tabacco leaves imported from Nexal were available for purchase through ''[[Aurora's Whole Realms Catalogue]]'' in the 1360s DR.

Imported ''balaumo'' was sold in cafes of [[Arrabar]] in the [[Vilhon Reach]] in the early 1370s DR. Namely, [[Efusio's Cafe]] offered a wide variety of fruit-infused tobacco blends, including [[cherry]], [[apricot]], [[apple]],

Some flavors of tobacco enjoyed by [[wizard]]s in [[Magician's Row]] in [[Ravens Bluff]] in the late 1350s DR were Bittersage, Dragonfire, Golden Sea, Old Troll, and Saltweed.<ref>{{Cite polyhedron/58/The Living City: Of Wits and Wizards, A Logic Puzzle|27}}
